    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape, just waiting for a new home. It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll feel that the moment you hop behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
