    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. This 4.0L powerplant features eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal lateral grip and torque distribution. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including throttle actuator replacement and a rod bearing health check. The 6-speed manual transmission offers short, precise throws, complemented by a dual-mass flywheel. While showing minor cosmetic patina expected of its age, the drivetrain remains robust with no signs of subframe fatigue. A purist-spec enthusiast vehicle optimized for performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
