    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips and the occasional weekend getaway. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! It drives like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
